claim: Tyra Banks was the second African American woman on the cover of GQ.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Born in Inglewood , California , she began her career as a model at age 15 , and was the first African American woman to be featured on the covers of GQ and the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue , on which she appeared twice .
